1329
01:17:35,923 --> 01:17:38,092
And tell that schmuck
to drop everything

1330
01:17:38,159 --> 01:17:40,595
and take my call
right the hell now.

1331
01:17:40,661 --> 01:17:42,531
-Of course.
-Thank you.

1332
